00:48:47.070 --> 00:48:48.440
Besides selling our book.

00:48:48.440 --> 00:48:49.900
You know, who cares?

00:48:49.900 --> 00:48:52.980
So just to summarize.

00:48:52.980 --> 00:48:56.040
But I think you've all
probably heard this before.

00:48:56.040 --> 00:48:59.980
First of all, mathematics
is the language of nature.

00:48:59.980 --> 00:49:02.480
