00:49:10.940 --> 00:49:11.770
But he didn't know.

00:49:11.770 --> 00:49:12.270
Yeah.

00:49:12.270 --> 00:49:14.491
Well it was very
insightful of him.

00:49:14.491 --> 00:49:14.990
Yeah.

00:49:14.990 --> 00:49:17.680
Mathematics is the
language of nature.

00:49:17.680 --> 00:49:20.900
And so, people who might not
be interested in mathematics

00:49:20.900 --> 00:49:23.900
per se-- I mean most people
are interested in some part

00:49:23.900 --> 00:49:26.620
of the natural world.

00:49:26.620 --> 00:49:28.370
And if you want to
be a good citizen,

00:49:28.370 --> 00:49:30.740
you need to know your
basic mathematics.

00:49:30.740 --> 00:49:32.570
And there's all these
horrible stories

00:49:32.570 --> 00:49:35.150
