about people don't

00:49:35.150 --> 00:49:36.730
have any financial literacy.

00:49:36.730 --> 00:49:38.710
They don't understand
compound interest.

00:49:38.710 --> 00:49:41.860
They don't understand
global warming.

00:49:41.860 --> 00:49:42.680
Things like that.

00:49:42.680 --> 00:49:45.340
All those kind of
things would be

00:49:45.340 --> 00:49:48.190
better served if we--
