00:49:48.190 --> 00:49:51.400
as a society are slowly moving
in the direction of making

00:49:51.400 --> 00:49:55.910
mathematics more accessible
and more fun for all people,

00:49:55.910 --> 00:50:00.250
not just for this 5% or 10%
who get born interested.

00:50:00.250 --> 00:50:02.760
And then, finally we
want to have people

00:50:02.760 --> 00:50:05.990
going into the STEM areas.

00:50:05.990 --> 00:50:07.820
We need more and
more people educated

00:50:07.820 --> 00:50:10.500
