and engineering, and so on.

00:50:10.500 --> 00:50:13.470
And so, you need a
bigger pool to draw from.

00:50:13.470 --> 00:50:16.302
So I think those are all good
reasons for writing books

00:50:16.302 --> 00:50:17.760
like these and
trying to get people

00:50:17.760 --> 00:50:19.300
interested in mathematics.

